{"tid":390700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★香港婦聯調查：逾七成港人家庭生活愉快 創四年新高","createTime":"2017-09-07T09:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T11:39:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c54ee3f192b4257183908ede7b9eabdf8ab2b85","tid":390700,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:13:56.000Z","msg":"香港婦聯公布「快樂家庭」問卷調查結果，當中發現有逾七成港人認為家庭生活愉快，數字為過去4年的新高，婦聯估計是因新政府班子推出的政策能回應市民，同時促請政府在下月公布的施政報告中，制訂更多家庭友善政策。<br />\n<br />\n香港婦聯社會政策研究委員會在今年7至8月，以問卷調查形式訪問490名市民，當中有七成二受訪者認為家庭生活愉快，數字比去年高出百分之八，創過去4年的新高。香港婦聯副主席歐陽寶珍表示，估計是因為新政府班子上任後，推出不少新政策，如：派發自資學士學位津貼，「實際回應了年青人的關注。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170906/_2017090613040111592.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170906%2F_2017090613040111592.jpeg&h=6c73ac28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/505698-香港-香港婦聯調查：逾七成港人家庭生活愉快+創四年新高\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F505698-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A9%A6%E8%81%AF%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%83%E6%88%90%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%84%89%E5%BF%AB%2B%E5%89%B5%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98&d=jAWKDuawMC2NgPjoHRY6Y0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=c8050595\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F505698-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A9%A6%E8%81%AF%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%83%E6%88%90%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%84%89%E5%BF%AB%2B%E5%89%B5%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98&h=57989909\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/505698-香港-香港婦聯調查：逾七成港人家庭生活愉快+創四年新高</a>"},{"pid":"9434b1d40eda52df05dbc2ce5d9196378dbc9f2c","tid":390700,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,